artists.biography: Not to be confused with Various Artists. Various was the original moniker of the English dubstep/electronic duo formed in 2003, more commonly known as Various Production. Their debut album, The World Is Gone was released under this name. Read more on Last.fm. User-contributed text is available under the Creative Commons By-SA License; additional terms may apply.
